    "developmentType": "residential_flat_building",
    "description": "A competition winning large lot development around a garden courtyard featuring one and two storey homes with dual aspects.",
    "designConcepts": [
      "Corner apartments and terrace-like row homes around a garden courtyard",
      "Clear block hierarchy: ground-floor entries activate primary streets",
      "Diverse mix of studio to 4-bedroom dwellings in 1 or 2-storey layouts",
      "Smart 2-storey apartments with living and sleeping on different levels",
      "Linear 'compactus' containing stairs, kitchens and bathrooms for efficient construction",
      "Sculptural landscape courtyard encouraging social interaction and green outlook"
    ],
